reviewText: THIS IS THE CLEAREST OF LEFTY'S VIDEOS, IT HELPS THAT JASON BORGER DIRECTED IT.  THEY MIGHT HAVE SPENT A BIT MORE TIME SHOOTING  THE INDIVIDUAL CASTS FROM OTHER POINTS OF VIEW, BUT YOU CAN SEE THE LINE MOVING WHICH HAS BEEN A PROBLEM IN OTHER VIDEOS.  NOW WHEN WILL IT BE MADE INTO A DVD?
